╣Joseph Rifkind & Renee Rifkind
Walked and sat here every day, it was their special place.
They are remembered by their children:
Marion, Gabrielle and Charles
and their 10 grandchildren"Į
║John, George, Paul & Ringo from The Beatles
Pop Group sat here during their
"MAD DAY OUT"
Sunday 28th of July 1968

Donated by caring neighbour Ted Baker
because he loves this park"Š
